collections.name: Tag
collections.description:
1. Letterform & Structure
The letters are compressed and interwoven, creating a compact and cohesive look.
The style is semi-wildstyle, with readable forms but enhanced by extensions and overlaps.
There’s a consistent stroke thickness, making the tag feel balanced and unified.
The horizontal flow makes the letters feel connected, almost like a continuous motion.
2. Connections & Flow
The first letter is tightly linked to the second, creating a sense of natural progression.
Some letters appear slightly stacked or overlapped, contributing to the layered depth of the tag.
The letters have a dynamic forward motion, where the eye is led smoothly from left to right.
3. Accents & Enhancements
Oval Enclosure: The surrounding shape gives structure to the tag, almost like a bubble that contains its energy. This technique makes the tag stand out while preventing it from feeling loose.

collections.name: Farm Guardians
collections.description:
Farm Guardians: NFT for the Care of Our Animals

In a world where the connection with nature is gradually being lost, a unique initiative is born to preserve and care for farm animals in a sustainable way. Guardians of the Farm is more than just a collection of NFTs; It is an invitation to be part of a noble cause: ensuring the well-being of our animals.

Each NFT represents a real inhabitant of our farm: horses, cows, sheep, chickens and more. By purchasing one, you not only become their digital protector, but you also directly contribute to their diet, health and quality of life. Additionally, holders of these NFTs will have access to a periodic check on the animal's status and the opportunity to visit it on the farm to see first-hand the impact of their support.

This collection is hosted on the Ethereum blockchain and available on OpenSea, guaranteeing transparency and authenticity in each transaction.

Join us and be part of this community of guardians
